PrecisApproval of the re-appointment by the Minister of Transport of JACQUELINE BOUTET, of Montreal, Quebec, BARBARA KANE, of Halifax, Nova Scotia, and ALAN CHAPPLE, of Toronto, Ontario, as directors of the Board of Directors of VIA Rail Canada Inc. to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
